meanings.definition: (Zoology) An unranked clade of gastropods containing the Heterobranchia and Caenogastropoda.
meanings.english_definition: An unranked clade of gastropods containing the Heterobranchia and Caenogastropoda.

etymology.value: From Latin *gressorius*, from *gressus* (“a going, walking”), past participle of *gradi* (“to walk, step”).
